(50, 'Hit ', '30.088568', '31.3191381', 0, '<p>HIT is a fitness entity that is affiliated with CrossFit. We deliver various fitness programs which suit different fitness levels. All our trainers are certified to train our athletes in a way that will move their body the way it&nbsp; &nbsp; ï¿½s meant to move. We believe that a healthy lifestyle is not a phase; its a journey that everyone should go through and have it facilitated for them to embrace. We train hard, because how we do anything is how we do everything</p>\r\n', NULL, '', '', 13, 'Heliopolis Sporting Club ', '01096498452', '', 'info@hitegypt.com', 'http://www.hitegypt.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/hitclanegypt', '', '', 'False', '', './images/activity_data_images/image048.png', './images/activity_data_images/thumb/582875_resized455085.jpg', '12', '7', '', 0, '', 'Show', 0, '', NULL, NULL, 'activity', NULL, NULL, '2019-01-13 12:15:36'),
