(56, 'Fight and Fitness Factory', '30.0203423', '31.0057257', 0, '<p>The first dedicated MMA &amp; Functional Training facility in Sheikh Zayed and Maadi, the Fight and Fitness Factory puts your health and well-being firmly at the top of the agenda. With a strong focus on mixed martial arts, the fastest growing sport worldwide, our professional trainers and fitness experts will tailor a program suited to your needs, abilities and aims. Combining the combat disciplines of Muay Thai, Kickboxing, Boxing, Grappling, and Jiu-Jitsu, as well as more specialized styles, MMA training combines a full mind and body workout, increasing endurance and toning all your muscles. Youll even get a chance to try out what youve learned in our official boxing ring and MMA cage. But were not just about fighting. Members are free to use our robust selection of gym equipment and are encouraged to try as many of our varied classes as possible. From spinning and circuit training to Boxercise&nbsp;and Yoga, theres an activity for everyone, even the kids. Services offered Mixed &nbsp;Fitness classes Kickoff, FX3, More 4 Core, Cal-burn, Spinning &amp; Fighting classes MMA, Muay Thai, Kickboxing, Boxing, Grappling, Jiu-Jitsu. Others Showers &amp; Lockers. Juice bar. Gym Area. MMA Ring. Cage area for Jiu-Jitsu and Muay Thai classes. Nutrition department. Open area workout area.</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 6, '6 October City-Arkan Mall, Cairo, Egypt', '01280501070', '', '', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/F3Egypt/', '', '', 'False', '', './images/activity_data_images/image069.png', './images/activity_data_images/thumb/397470_resized693114.jpg', '16', '7', 'Sunday to Wednesday : 7:00 am - 11:00 pmTursday : 7:00 am - 9:00 pmFriday : 2pm till 9pmSaturday : 9:00 am till 11:00 pm', 0, '', 'Show', 0, '', NULL, NULL, 'activity', NULL, NULL, '2018-12-08 14:23:55'),
