(67, 'Golds Gym', '30.0529786', '31.1955527', 0, '<p><em>Gold&rsquo;s Gym has been the authority on fitness since 1965. It was then that fitness legend Joe Gold took the knowledge and expertise he gained from training at the world famous &ldquo;Muscle Beach&rdquo; and opened up the first Gold&rsquo;s Gym on Pacific Avenue in Venice, California.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Opened long before the modern day health club existed, the original Gold&rsquo;s Gym featured homemade equipment and an unrivaled dedication to getting results. It was an instant hit. Early fitness enthusiasts flocked to the gym, and in 1977, Gold&rsquo;s Gym received international attention from &ldquo;Pumping Iron&rdquo; &ndash; a bodybuilding documentary starring Arnold Schwarzenegger and Lou Ferrigno.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>With its storied reputation of being THE place to go for the latest training techniques, and its legendary history of producing bodybuilding champions, Gold&rsquo;s Gym Venice became known as &ldquo;The Mecca Of Bodybuilding.&rdquo; Hollywood celebrities and professional athletes soon followed and by 1980, Gold&rsquo;s Gym began expanding to locations around the globe.</em></p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, '18 Damascus St. Off Syria St., Mohandeseen, Giza.', '01140100666', '0233036663', '', 'https://www.goldsgym.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/GoldsGymEgypt/', '', '', 'False', '', './images/activity_data_images/image081.png', './images/activity_data_images/thumb/554303_resized947654.jpg', '18', '7', '6:00 am - 12:00 am', 0, '', 'Show', 0, '', NULL, NULL, 'activity', NULL, NULL, '2018-12-29 11:10:21'),
