(131, 'Groovy Medical Aesthetic Spa', '30.0874985', '31.3302798', 0, '<p><em>Ever since its inception,&nbsp;<strong>GROOVY&nbsp;</strong>has been all about feeling good on the inside and the outside. At Groovy, we don&rsquo;t just focus on one body part &ndash; we strive on delivering a sense of well being to the body as a whole. Our state of the art, medical-grade spa services are scientifically designed to administer treatments for the entire human body.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Products and services at Groovy range from skin-care treatments such as derma fillers and laser procedures all the way to nutritional services, spa treatments, and a complete, modern gym. What distinguishes Groovy from other spas is our professionalism and medical standard. The medical services that Groovy offers are of the same caliber as any medical clinic or hospital.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Any services provided at Groovy are constantly under the supervision of doctors and medical professionals with vast experience in the field who endeavor to provide effectual and safe procedures for every client.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>At Groovy, we pride ourselves on creating the most relaxing and comfortable atmosphere possible because nothing matters to us more than helping you fall in love with yourself.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Your confidence is our profit!&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 12, '9 Ibn Batota, off Salah Salem, Heliopolis, Cairo.', '01114499213 ', '16914', 'info@groovymedspa.com', 'http://www.groovymedspa.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/groovymedspa/', '', '', 'False', '', './images/activity_data_images/Groovy logo.jpg', './images/activity_data_images/thumb/873519_resized466685.jpg', '12', '7', '10:00 AM -10:00 PM ', 0, '', 'Show', 0, '', NULL, NULL, 'doctor', NULL, NULL, '2018-12-08 14:24:54'),
