(135, 'CrossFit Rhea', '30.0604142', '30.9607769', 0, '<p>In Greek mythology, RHEA is known as the mother of the Olympian gods. The descendants of the Olympian divinities include gods and goddess like: Heracles god of power, Athena goddess of wisdom, and Nike goddess of victory. ï¿½Give me a place to stand and a lever long enough and I will move the worldï¿½ -ARCHIMEDES, 220 BC, in praise of RHEA. The Olympian gods have always symbolized the human kind stages of transformation to finding fulfillment. CrossFit RHEA stands for the psychological drive to transform. For the integration of mind and body, and for pushing limits and boundaries. In our CrossFit box, we aspire our members to achieve their highest potential. We put great efforts and programs to achieve physical strength, agility, and endurance combined with mental sharpness, discipline, and focus. Whatever you are striving to achieve, at Crossfit RHEA, there is a relentless pursuit of a goal and for achieving real results. No matter what is your background in sports or how active is your daily life, we will take care of your fitness needs, individually or in groups so you can grow healthier and stronger every day. Services CrossFit (Mixed classes, Ladies only, Kids and Teens, Beginners and fundamentals) Weightlifting Speciality Classes Yoga Ladies only Kids Kickboxing Personal Training</p>\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, 'Beverly Hills compound, Gate 5,The Walk Mall, Building 10, Sheikh Zayed City, Egypt', '01207343215', '', '', 'https://crossfitrhea.wordpress.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/CrossFitRHEA/', '', '', 'False', '', './images/activity_data_images/image148.png', './images/activity_data_images/thumb/26975_resized226073.jpg', '13', '6', '9:00 AM - 10:00 PM', 0, '', 'Show', 0, '', NULL, NULL, 'activity', NULL, NULL, '2018-12-29 11:11:07'),
