(191, 'Power House Gym', '30.0204421', '31.0048037', 0, '<p>Powerhouse Gym (PHG) is the worldï¿½s pioneer in the fitness industry. With more than 300 gyms all over the world, PHG has gone global and expanded into 17 countries worldwide. Powerhouse Gym provides world class services to all its members ranging from fitness enthusiasts to professional athletes. The PHG brand name is associated with exceptional service and genuine quality. Our unique atmosphere, knowledgeable staff, and premier exercise equipment has made us the fastest growing international gym chain in the world. Powerhouse Gym enables its members to reach their fitness goals and change their lifestyles forever; we offer a holistic fitness experience for our valued members, not just another workout routine. Powerhouse Gym Sheikh Zayed has been designed by a world class architect to create an upbeat and unique atmosphere never before seen in Egypt and the Middle East. PHG Sheikh Zayed is a luxurious, fully equipped 10,000 Square feet facility that includes: ï¿½ Executive style locker rooms ï¿½ Fully equipped workout area with top of the line Life Fitness equipment ï¿½ Cutting edge cardio equipment that identifies each member ï¿½ Spacious group fitness studio with innovative daily classes ï¿½ Spinning classes ï¿½ Pro Bar &amp; Lounge ï¿½ Official PHG Pro Shop ï¿½ Elite personal trainers ï¿½ Qualified nutritionists ï¿½ Professional physiotherapists ï¿½ Sauna &amp; steam rooms ï¿½ Private solarium with top of the line tanning equipment ï¿½ Massage Treatment</p>\r\n', '1900', '4900', '7100', 8, 'Al Guezira Plaza Tower 1, First Floor, Sheikh Zayed, 6 October City', '01000601590', '', '', 'https://www.powerhousegymegypt.com/', 'https://www.facebook.com/powerhousegymegypt/', '', '', 'False', '', './images/activity_data_images/image199.png', './images/activity_data_images/thumb/67708_resized784644.jpg', '19', '7', ' 6:00AM ï¿½ 1:00AM', 0, '', 'Show', 0, '', NULL, NULL, 'activity', NULL, NULL, '2018-12-08 14:19: