(189, 'My thoughts today, what makes a person happy or unhappy?', 'My thoughts today, what makes a person happy or unhappy?', '2-My thoughts today, what makes a person happy or unhappy?\r\n\r\nWhat makes them lost or not?\r\n\r\nIs it people in their lives? Is it things they have or want?\r\n\r\nI believe it&rsquo;s way beyond that, took me awhile to realize that you re never truly happy, unless you re in peace with your own self, when you re content with the way your life is and keeps unfolding, when you see the good things in people and the good things you have in your life\r\n\r\nAs Humans, it&rsquo;s second nature to dwell on the little things, things that yes are a part of our life but don&rsquo;t shape up our lives entirely.\r\n\r\nIt&rsquo;s also in our blood to let our ego takeover our actions and emotions.\r\n\r\nI think Inner contentment takes time to find and keep, However it&rsquo;s always a question of how much you re willing to look and explore. And to act from a place of love, everyday. &hearts;️\r\n\r\n#Happiness #Thoughts #Contentment #Love #Humans #Souls #Peace #Yoga #MindBodySoul\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n', 13, 41, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2022-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/unnamed (5).jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/867351_resized538322.jpg', 0, 'True'),
