(194, 'Whatever happens in your life today, or didn’t happen it doesn’t matter', 'Whatever happens in your life today, or didn’t happen it doesn’t matter', '7-Whatever happens in your life today, or didn&rsquo;t happen it doesn&rsquo;t matter.&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nYou don&rsquo;t have to wait for perfection in order to accept yourself. &hearts;️\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nAcceptance does not mean finality, wherever you are in your life today is perfect.&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n#Acceptance #Love #SelfLove #Perfection #Finality #Peacefulness #LastDayIn2018 #ShowSomeLove #Today #Life #BackBends #HeartOpeners #Yoga #MindBodySoul\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\r\n', 13, 41, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2022-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/unnamed (10).jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/768257_resized944650.jpg', 0, 'True'),
