(206, 'Stepping stones.', 'Stepping stones.', '19-Stepping stones.\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nI truly believe that everything in life, has many stepping stones.&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nNothing happens overnight.\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nDecisions maybe instant but progress over time...\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nYou eat health, you feel healthier week by week.\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nYou move the body, you grow energy day by day.\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nYou start reading, you grow knowledge and wisdom over time.\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nYou get feelings, you fall in love in phases.&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nTrust the process of unfolding and revealing, It shall happen in stepping stones.&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n#SteppingStones #TheProcess #Phases #BeanosFitDiaries #Wellness #Health #Love #SelfLove #Yoga #MindBodySoul\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\r\n', 13, 41, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2022-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/unnamed (22).jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/156525_resized52686.jpg', 0, 'False'),
(207, 'Alice in MARRAKECH', 'Alice in MARRAKECH', '1-Join me and my Yogi soulmate Yoga With Alice in MARRAKECH for a colorful and transformational 8-day, 7-night journey through the chakras. Yoga offerings and daily activities will build upon each other and progress from the root chakra to the crown, so you leave feeling balanced, liberated and empowered. From laid back days around the pool to bargaining for authentic goods in town; an excursion to the Atlas Mountains and even a Moroccan cooking class &amp; a spa day, this retreat has it all. Yoga classes will range from yin to high intensity vinyasa and everywhere in between. All classes are suitable for all levels- we think an immersive week learning about the chakras is a perfect way to start your yoga practice! FOR MORE INFO &amp; BOOKINGS: Check out the link right here&nbsp;&nbsp;https://smex12-5-en-ctp.trendmicro.com:443/wis/clicktime/v1/query?url=https%3a%2f%2falicesatlas.com%2fretreats%2f&amp;umid=426bf033-2f09-4d72-b64f-97690c0a5eee&amp;auth=28023ff380bd1758b83b3ca3dae822401115e117-d28588a5933918289f48e2202eb4ce29a8021ed5\r\n\r\n#YogaRetreats #Morocco #Marrakech #Yoga #Chakras #Soulmates #Transform #Travel #Practice #Teach #Love #MindBodySoul @ Marrakech-Moroco&nbsp;\r\n', 13, 42, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2022-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/unnamed (2).jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/669076_resized398996.jpg', 0, 'True'),
(208, 'As a Health Coach and Yoga Teacher', 'As a Health Coach and Yoga Teacher', '2-As a Health Coach and Yoga Teacher, Bringing Wellness into Schools and Leading Nutrition and Yoga Workshops to create awareness amongst the Students and growing generations has been something I&rsquo;ve longed for!&nbsp; Growing up, I wish that would ve taken place at my school! Some enlightenment on eating habits, patterns, body movement, body awareness, peace of mind and body and mind connection.&nbsp; And it&rsquo;s finally happening at The International School of Coueifat, For their Cairo Health Week Awareness! Let&rsquo;s make a difference!&nbsp; #Schools #HealthWeekAwareness #TheInternationalSchoolOfCoueifat #NutritionAndYogaWorkshop #LetsMakeADifference #Teacher #Server #HealthCoach #Wellness #Student\r\n', 13, 42, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2022-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/unnamed (23).jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/84935_resized601637.jpg', 0, 'True'),
