(210, ' Lets Get High!', ' Lets Get High!', '4- Lets Get High! || Sunset Arm Balance Workshop&nbsp;TOMORROW ; Tuesday the 14th at 6:00 PM, A 90 mins Workshop, at Telal Sahel by the beach!&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLove to fly and practice arm balances? The problem is that there is never enough time to practice them during a yoga class nor for the instructor to share all the details while flowing through the cues.\r\n\r\nWhether you&rsquo;re a seasoned practitioner or a beginner, this workshop will help you strengthen and develop a mindful arm balance practice - all levels welcome!\r\n\r\nIn this workshop, we will start with a fun flow to build heat and connect with the breath, followed by a step-by-step tutorial on the mechanics, anatomy, and kinesiology of the most common non-inverted arm balances as well as wrist exercises to release stress and promote a healthy foundation on the hands.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nYou will learn how to properly warm up your body and practice safely as you begin to take flight.\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nThis is a practical workshop so pack your water and get ready to sweat and fly. You will leave this workshop inspired and ready to take your practice to the next level!\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nSpace is limited. Reserve your spot now by sending at DM or By Emailing at; Edenwellnesseg.com&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n#Eden #EdenWellness #FeelsLikeOm #ArmBalances #Workshop #LetsGetHigh #Sunset #Strength #Practice #Fly #Core #Connect #Arms #TelalSahel #Sahel #Yogis #Teach #Learn #Anatomy #Mechanics #Invert\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\r\n', 13, 42, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2022-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/unnamed (25).jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/281271_resized776994.jpg', 0, 'True'),
