(225, 'Pyramids Marathon 2019', 'The Pyramids Marathon takes place on February 15th, 2019', '<p><em>The Pyramids Marathon takes place on February 15th, 2019, inviting runners from around the world to run at the most iconic of locations: the Great Pyramids of Giza. Egypt&rsquo;s signature running event doesn&rsquo;t just offer the 42K, but also the 21K and 10K distances, meaning anyone can take part and run through 5000 years of history. Sign up today and&nbsp;#RaceThroughHistory!</em></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>The Pyramids Marathon is proudly organised by&nbsp;The TriFactory.The TriFactory is an Egyptian sports management company specialising in endurance sports and mass participation sports events.</em></p>\\r\\n', 18, 46, 'True', '2019-02-15', '2019-02-20', './images/newsCms/Data/Pyramids-Run-1392x783.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/749410_resized122429.jpg', 2, 'True'),
