(241, 'WEEK 1 DAY 1   (DUMBBELL BENCH PRESS)', '2 SETS, REPS 10/set', '<p><em>1. Lie back on a flat bench with a dumbbell in each hand.<br />\\r\\n2. Hold the weights at shoulder level and then press the weights straight over your chest.</em></p>\\r\\n', 17, 53, 'True', '2019-12-10', '2029-12-10', '', '', 0, 'True');
