(370, 'Simeon Panda', '    ', '<p><em>Simeon Panda is one of the most influential fitness professionals in the world. Owner of Just Lift.&reg; and SP Aesthetics&reg; Sportswear, he is a fitness entrepreneur who is featured on Forbes as one of the worlds top ten influencers for fitness. Simeon has immense popularity not just because of his amazing physique, but for his character and high standards in representing the sports fitness industry.</em></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>With a social media following in excess of 10 million, he is respected for many reasons amongst his fans and followers worldwide, not least because of his highly positive and motivational approach to everything he does. He has competed in Musclemania&reg; competitions worldwide, winning the European Championship and earning himself Musclemania Pro&reg; status. He regularly judges physique, modelling and bodybuilding shows all over the world.</em></p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Simeon has hosted seminars and workshops around the world including the Mr Olympia Weekend. He has graced the front covers, written for and been featured in major fitness publications worldwide such as Muscle &amp; Fitness, MuscleMag, Muscle-Insider, Train Mag, Muscle &amp; Performance, Fitness RX to name a few. He has appeared live on Australia&rsquo;s Number one national breakfast tv show &lsquo;The Today Show,&rsquo; New Yorks most popular urban radio station &lsquo;Hot 97,&rsquo; he has also hosted seminars in countries all over the world.</em></p>\\r\\n', 10, 77, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2029-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/48270259_2119786068084062_5685697806891745280_n.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/172442_resized375409.jpg', 0, 'True'),
(371, 'Sergi Constance', '    ', '<p><em>Sergi Constance 24 years fitness model and men physique competitor from Spain, currently at EEUU, in Miami and New York, and looking for sponsors. His ultimate&nbsp;goal is bodybuilding to get better and better aesthetic body. He wants to succeed as a bodybuilder while still Maintaining good athletic skills and good looks<br />\\r\\nSergi Constance 24 a&ntilde;os, modelo fitness y competidor men physique y culturismo, de Valencia, Espa&ntilde;a.<br />\\r\\nbuscando sponsor. Su objetivo actual es mejorar f&iacute;sicamente su cuerpo, llegando a ser un culturista manteniendo sus cualidades atl&eacute;ticas y una buena apariencia.</em></p>\\r\\n', 10, 77, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2029-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/1116118_492384670839921_1996346046_o.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/874332_resized616419.jpg', 0, 'True'),
(372, 'Ulisses', '    ', '<p><em>Ulisses is a celebrity trainer, professional bodybuilding champion and international fitness model. In between travelling as a celebrity trainer on celebrity tours and movie shoots, and being featured in countless fitness magazines throughout America and Europe, Ulisses has been a master trainer and co- manager of an elite health club in New York and has also successfully run his own personal training studio gym business in New York &amp; London. Ulisses is known for his effective yet easy techniques, practised by hundreds of his clients, many of them celebrities who rely on his workouts for their ongoing success as well-known &lsquo;hot-bodies&rsquo;. His personable approach and his own dedication to health and well being plays a massive part in his success, and fitness magazines worldwide often feature his tips and exercise routines that can easily be incorporated into today&rsquo;s hectic schedules. He is a Musclemania Super Body &amp; World Pro Champion winner! Ulisses has a training studio for clients in London and New York.</em></p>\\r\\n', 10, 77, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2029-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/13754582_1153500514720592_2654869739619144158_n.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/65460_resized398103.jpg', 0, 'True'),
(373, 'Lazar Angelov', '     ', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em>Before becoming a bodybuilder and a personal trainer, Lazar Angelov played professional basketball for 10 years. He led his team in scoring for multiple seasons&nbsp;and was one of the best point guards of his class. At the age of 16 he joined the junior national team of Bulgaria and played for a couple of teams in the National Basketball Association of Bulgaria. At the age of 18 he spent an year and a half in the Army, where he found his vocation &ndash; bodybuilding. It became a constant part of his life and he went on to earn a certificate for a personal trainer from the National Sports Academy. Lazar started working with people, helping them to reach their maximum potential in developing their bodies.<br />\\r\\nHe dedicated his life to bodybuilding and since 2006 has been taking part in different competitions, while never failing to win at least a bronze medal every time. He achieved that despite never taking (and never will) steroids. Lazar dominates other bodybuilders with balanced physique and incredible definition.<br />\\r\\nHe owns some of the best abs in the world. As a personal trainer he has been able to transform the bodies of thousands of people and to make his motivation and knowledge contagious to them. As a model he takes part in a number of music videos and advertisements. His body, his ambition and his motivation are inspiration to millions of people around the world thanks to his youtube videos. Due to the thousands of questions and inquiries about his every day training and nutrition he decided to create his personal website &ndash;&nbsp;lazarangelov.com, where everyone will have the chance to receive everything needed for reaching the maximum physical potential without using steroids.<br />\\r\\nIn January, 2012 Lazar Angelov joined Nutri-sups Worldwide - the #1 supplement distribution company in the world.</em></p>\\r\\n', 10, 77, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2029-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/1743724_1039641229385804_6464919318791381387_n.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/775347_resized142230.jpg', 0, 'True'),
(374, 'Jaco de Bruyn', '    ', '<p><em>Jaco de Bruyn is one of the fastest growing Muscle models in the world and nominated at the most influential WBFF Pros ever! The South African icon is an internationally acclaimed leader in the fitness world. For Jaco de Bruyn, fitness is a way of life thus he maintains his promotable and photogenic physique all year round. Not only is his mission in life to inspire young individuals but he always tried and send a positive message out to the world on a daily basis. Jaco de Bruyn takes his training very seriously and has years of experience as a model, celebrity icon, husband, father of 2, personal trainer, and motivational speaker to many worldwide.<br />\\r\\nHis focus and approach to health, fitness, inspiring people and training individuals to achieve their upmost best in this industry coupled with his detailed knowledge of nutritional excellence, has given him the title of one of the most aesthetic and perfectly sculpted physiques in the world. Competitively, Jaco de Bruyn is a WBFF PRO Muscle Model. He is one of the world&rsquo;s top ranked aesthetic models, he is a recognized international bodybuilding superstar. He regularly appears on numerous South African, USA, European and Australian platforms. He makes guest appearances at fitness expo&rsquo;s, celebrity tours and other events throughout the world.<br />\\r\\nJaco de Bruyn inspires thousands of people through leadership and example, educating young followers to reach bigger highest and to follow their dreams. He&rsquo;s a guy that wants to leave a legacy behind not only as an fitness icon but as a father and husband to his loved ones helping them surpass their training goals focused and healthy way.<br />\\r\\nFavorite Quote?<br />\\r\\n&lsquo;&rsquo;Desire is the key to motivation, but it&rsquo;s the determination and commitment to an unrelenting pursuit of your goal &ndash; a commitment to excellence &ndash; that will enable you to attain the success you seek</em></p>\\r\\n', 10, 77, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2029-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/43756758_1990358307720876_5904512449159102464_n.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/858709_resized407887.jpg', 0, 'True'),
(375, 'Jeff Seid', '    ', '<p><em>22 year old natural bodybuilder who has dedicated 11 years to bodybuilding, aspiring to build the perfect physique &amp; promote a healthy aesthetic lifestyle.</em></p>\\r\\n', 10, 77, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2029-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/13220924_968342263271205_6079749851131082401_n.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/205342_resized624177.jpg', 0, 'True'),
(376, 'Alon Gabbay', '    ', 'My name is Alon Gabbay and in addition to being a fitness model and a&nbsp;natural bodybuilder, I&#39;m an artist, musician, photographer and photo editor, video editor, and web and graphic designer.\r\n\r\nI have a passion for anything related to aesthetics, whether it&#39;s my own body or art that I&#39;m creating. I love what I do and that is what keep me motivated.\r\n\r\nI&#39;m half Israeli half German, what a combination, huh? I Was born in Germany but raised in Israel, living back in Germany now.\r\n\r\nMy love for bodybuilding began when I turned 17, and since that time, no one has been able to get the dumbbells out of my hands!\r\n\r\nI have never competed in any bodybuilding competitions. I am just doing it for myself - for the love of the sport, for my body and soul, and for my own satisfaction. Although I have never stood on a stage, I still see myself as a professional, who learned, trained, and studied the art of bodybuilding all the way, transforming it from a hobby into a way of life.\r\n\r\nMy goal in bodybuilding is to achieve the best I can as a&nbsp;natural bodybuilder, as well as to stay healthy and strong.\r\n\r\nBasically anything you see from me has been made by me. I made my own website, edit my own videos, take my own pictures, and train by myself in the gym.\r\n\r\nIf you like any of my work , feel free to subscribe to my website by using the email form below.\r\n\r\nYours truly, Alon Gabbay, SiX PACK\r\n', 10, 77, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2029-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/19143172_1400868823282007_6560679611309424578_o.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/771496_resized687355.jpg', 0, 'True'),
(377, 'Chul Soon', '     ', 'Musclemania&reg; Pro Chul Soon is among the most popular natural bodybuilders and sports models in the world. The Seoul, South Korea native is an internationally acclaimed leader in the fitness world.\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nChul Soon is a Musclemania World Pro and Model Korea Champion. He is a celebrity fitness trainer and makes frequent appearances in Korean commercials, advertisements, magazines, and television shows.\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\nBodybuilding and Fitness Competitions\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\r\n\r\n&bull; 2016 Musclemania Universe at Fitness Universe, Professional Medium, 1st place - Overall Champion &bull; 2015 Musclemania Universe at Fitness Universe, Professional Medium, 1st place - Overall Champion &bull; 2015 Musclemania World at Fitness America Weekend, Professional Medium, 2nd place &bull; 2014 Musclemania Universe at Fitness Universe, Professional Medium, 1st place &bull; 2013 Musclemania World at Fitness America Weekend, Professional Medium, 2nd place &bull; 2012 Musclemania World at Fitness America Weekend, Professional Heavyweight, 1st place - Overall Champion &bull; 2011 Musclemania World at Fitness America Weekend, Professional Heavyweight, 4th place &bull; 2010 Musclemania World at Fitness America Weekend, Lightweight, World Champion (Pro Card Acquisition) &bull; 2010 Model Universe at Fitness Universe , 3rd place &bull; 2010 Musclemania Universe at Fitness Universe, Lightweight, 4th place &bull; 2010 Musclemania Universe Korea, Sports Model, 1st place &bull; 2009 Musclemania World at Fitness America Weekend, Lightweight, 2nd place &bull; 2009 Fitness Korea, Sports Model, 3rd place\r\n\r\n\\r\\n\r\n', 10, 77, 'True', '2019-01-10', '2029-12-10', './images/newsCms/Data/10348534_1597508473805390_8762624756496983296_n.jpg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/405684_resized812678.jpg', 0, 'True'),
