(385, 'Khabib Nurmagomedov announces his ideal next three fights; St-Pierre, Ferguson & Mayweather. ', '', '&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t know right now, but why not maybe (Georges) St.-Pierre, (Tony) Ferguson and (Floyd) Mayweather?&rdquo; Nurmagomedov said. &ldquo;It will be these three guys, and we can retire and become the greatest athlete of all time.&rdquo;\r\n\r\nThis isn&rsquo;t the first time Nurmagomedov has expressed interest in facing these three fighters. UFC President Dana White previously has stated&nbsp;he believes Ferguson deserves the next shot&nbsp;at Nurmagomedov&rsquo;s title, but the fight has been booked and subsequently canceled four times before. Although any hesitation would be understandable, it&rsquo;s clear Ferguson (24-3 MMA, 14-1 UFC) remains a top target for Nurmagomedov.\r\n\r\nAs for fighting St-Pierre (26-2 MMA, 20-2 UFC), it would check all the boxes for Nurmagomedov: legacy, money and&nbsp;an intriguing matchup. The only requirement would seem to be that it takes place at 155 pounds.\r\n', 6, 59, 'True', '2019-01-21', '2021-01-21', './images/newsCms/Data/Khabib.jpeg', './images/newsCms/Data/thumb/518457_resized545640.jpg', 0, 'True'),
