(28, '2018-11-24', '2018-12-10', 'Yoga Teacher Training', 'News', '<p>Become an internationally certified and registered yoga instructor at the Yoga Alliance with Hassina and Terhi!<br />\r\nThis course will teach you all the basics and understandings of yoga from November 24th till December 10th.<br />\r\nWhat will you learn?<br />\r\n* Techniques, training &amp; practice<br />\r\n* Teaching methodology<br />\r\n* Anatomy &amp; physiology<br />\r\n* Yoga Philosophy<br />\r\n* Practicum<br />\r\nWhy choose YTT?<br />\r\nAt YTT Journey, you learn to teach a general yoga class with a fusion of styles.<br />\r\nAbout the Teachers:<br />\r\nHassina Mircia-Albukhary &amp; Terhi Mengel are registered yoga teachers (RYT) with yoga alliance, which acknowledges the completion of a yoga teachers training with a registered yoga school (RYS).<br />\r\nIf you&rsquo;re a passionate aspiring yogi, sign up today to secure your spot!&nbsp;<br />\r\nCall us at 0122 9101901 for more info.<br />\r\nNamaste to all!&nbsp;</p>', './images/news/7ed34fd593da79c1c2907171821b8464.png', './images/news/thumb/resize_7ed34fd593da79c1c2907171821b8464.png', '2018-09-15 04:00:32', '2018-11-27 16:11:54', 1000000, '201', 0, 0),
(29, '2018-12-10', '2018-12-14', 'Yoga Retreat', 'News', '<p>For a grandiose finale to your course, join us in this purifying retreat from the 10th to the 14th of December.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA YOGI&rsquo;S JOURNEY THROUGH ANCIENT EGYPT&rsquo;S TREASURES ACROSS THE NILE RIVER.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSubscription deadline for members &amp; non-members: 15th of November<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCall us at 0122 9101901 for more info.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', './images/news/4f8f359abe030b37ed1ab9c51564b27e.jpg', './images/news/thumb/resize_4f8f359abe030b37ed1ab9c51564b27e.jpg', '2018-09-15 04:01:28', '2018-11-27 16:11:54', 1000000, '201', 0, 0),
