(80, '2018-11-21', '2018-11-24', 'Sahl Hasheesh Endurance Festival', 'News', '<p>For the fifth year running Egypt&rsquo;s finest Red Sea resort, Sahl Hasheesh, will host triathletes from all across the country and region for the 7th edition of the Sahl Hasheesh Endurance Festival. Last year&rsquo;s edition was the biggest triathlon/multi-sport event ever to take place in Egypt with over 1000 athletes from 30 different nationalities competing in the overall and age group standings.<strong>More Details:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cairogyms.com/event/sahl-hasheesh-endurance-festival/\">Click Here</a></p>\r\n', './images/news_images/TriFactory-Sahl-Hasheesh.jpg', './images/news_images/thumb/927867_resized404207.jpg', '2018-11-19 05:51:45', '2018-11-27 16:11:54', 1000000, '0', 0, 0),
(81, '2018-12-21', '2018-11-24', 'ELFIT Reebok 2018', 'Events', '<p>Adrenaline pumping, hands up in the air, screaming your favorite athlete&rsquo;s name at the top of your lungs, excitement, thrills, PRs broken infront of you, borders smashed and ALOT of fun with people ALL around.<br />\r\nYou&rsquo;ll be experiencing all this and more in every second of ELFIT.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Returning for its 6th season, ELFIT Reebok is an international fitness competition that&rsquo;s unique in the way it combines the elements of a thrilling competition, an exceptional community and an overall amazing spirit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ELFIT Reebok will take place on the 22nd, 23rd &amp; 24th of November, where cross fit athletes, from all over the world from more than 40 countries are coming down to the beautiful city of Hurghada along Egypt&rsquo;s mesmerizing red-sea coast to battle it out at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/senzosportingclub/\" target=\"_blank\">Senzo Sporting Club</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not only will every single event be extremely enjoyable and exciting to watch, but you will also be meeting a lot of people from the fitness community (athletes , spectators, organizers and volunteers) from different countries, where everyone shares their love for fitness, health and well-being.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Plus you will be enjoying ELFIT cool vibes, inspiring atmosphere, a festival of respect to every sweat drop every muscle cramp every cry of celebration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just by having the spectator&rsquo;s ticket, you will automatically enter the draw to win some really cool gifts&mdash; if you&rsquo;re lucky! Many sponsors will be giving away gifts for our crowd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aside from exciting entertainment pieces in our breaks, there&rsquo;ll be sponsors and vendors from all over the world in this area to showcase their products and have activations and games and small contests with awesome prizes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And of course, there&rsquo;ll be food!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ELFIT&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ReebokMENA/\" target=\"_blank\">Reebok</a>&nbsp;is an experience you surely don&rsquo;t want to miss!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Get your tickets now from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Ticketsmarche/\" target=\"_blank\">Ticketsmarche.com</a>&nbsp;for more info and booking call 16826:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ticketsmarche.com/elfit-reebok-2018_se_2010.html?fbclid=IwAR3mB6s1VqOQLydZEQSBApgcMznxNXgKlSaEqMt8ia_wyNLD0Ln3u6W_u8A\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ticketsmarche.com/elfit-reebok-2018_se_2010.html</a></p>\r\n', './images/news_images/ElFit-2018-1392x783.jpg', './images/news_images/thumb/385793_resized126383.jpg', '2018-11-19 05:55:51', '2018-11-28 04:59:53', 8, '0', 0, 0),
(82, '2018-12-14', '2018-12-14', 'ALEX Marathon!', 'Events', '<p>WE&rsquo;RE WELCOMING WINTER OUR OWN SPECIAL WAY!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s the perfect time for our First Alexandria Full Marathon.<br />\r\nDate:<br />\r\nFriday 14th of December.<br />\r\nLocation:<br />\r\nAlexandria Stadium.<br />\r\nThe Story behind the Marathon:<br />\r\nThe stadium is the oldest stadium in Egypt and Africa, it was built in 1929.<br />\r\nThe Marathon gate which is Gate no.6 has the exact same design as the Marathon Gate at Los Angeles Stadium.<br />\r\nKing Foad was the one who held the opening of the Stadium.<br />\r\nWe take it from here,<br />\r\nThis is the first time a race is held there.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Marathon Details:<br />\r\nThis marathon is special, it&rsquo;s starting point is the same as the ending point, which is the Marathon Gate of Alexandria Stadium &ldquo;Gate no.6&rdquo;<br />\r\nIt includes 5 Races:<br />\r\n42KM<br />\r\n21KM<br />\r\nFun Run<br />\r\nFamily Run<br />\r\nParalympic Race.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Registration through our website:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.cairorunners.com/alex2018?fbclid=IwAR1EK-nDIZiu8XAFZJIDrMJOgmta2DkaLq0rdxxMWeBp8k_feGaEMoY9PZQ\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cairorunners.com/alex2018</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>*TICKETS ARE NON REFUNDABLE*</p>\r\n', './images/news_images/Alex-Marathon-1392x783.jpg', './images/news_images/thumb/467360_resized746598.jpg', '2018-11-19 06:05:39', '2018-11-27 16:11:53', 1000000, '0', 0, 0),
(83, '2019-01-11', '2019-01-11', 'Marathon Cairo V', 'Events', '<p><em>This year, we&#39;re about breaking out of the limits, and carrying on beyond it. As running became a habit on our<br />\r\nbeautiful streets, running full and half marathons are now a habit for our fifth round of the all Egyptian &quot;Marathon Cairo&quot; in the middle east&#39;s capital. This year we have 4 events&nbsp;<br />\r\n1. Ultra Marathon 50K (Start 5:30)&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. Full Marathon 42K (Start 5:45)&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. Half Marathon 21K (start 7:00)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Follow the Event Page for all details and agenda</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>We will start from Masala Garden in Zamalek&nbsp;<br />\r\nRegistration will be open on Dec 4</em></p>\r\n', './images/news_images/Marathon-Cairo (1).jpg', './images/news_images/thumb/17719_resized974445.jpg', '2018-11-19 06:14:04', '2018-12-03 12:23:33', 7, '0', 0, 0),
(84, '2019-02-15', '2019-02-15', 'Pyramids Marathon 2019', 'Events', '<p><em>The Pyramids Marathon takes place on February 15th, 2019, inviting runners from around the world to run at the most iconic of locations: the Great Pyramids of Giza. Egypt&rsquo;s signature running event doesn&rsquo;t just offer the 42K, but also the 21K and 10K distances, meaning anyone can take part and run through 5000 years of history. Sign up today and&nbsp;#RaceThroughHistory!</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>The Pyramids Marathon is proudly organised by&nbsp;The TriFactory. The TriFactory is an Egyptian sports management company specialising in endurance sports and mass participation sports events.</em></p>\r\n', './images/news_images/Pyramids-Run-1392x783.jpg', './images/news_images/thumb/743240_resized95386.jpg', '2018-11-19 06:18:13', '2018-12-23 09:06:42', 2, '0', 0, 0),
(85, '2019-03-07', '2019-03-09', 'International Sports & Fitness North Africa', 'Events', '<p><em>North Africa&rsquo;s largest trade show for the sport and fitness</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Download your copy of the 2019 Event Brochure today to learn more about International Sports &amp; Fitness North Africa.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><a href=\"http://www.isf-northafrica.com/download-brochure\" target=\"_blank\">www.isf-northafrica.com/download-brochure</a></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Don&rsquo;t forget to book your ticket now</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', './images/news_images/International-Sports-and-Fitness-North-Africs.jpg', './images/news_images/thumb/24754_resized885030.jpg', '2018-11-19 06:21:43', '2018-12-23 09:07:24', 5, '0', 0, 0),
(86, '2018-11-04', '2018-11-04', 'Tycoons Tribe: From Alexandriaâ€™s leading fitness community to ElFit', 'News', '<p><em>CrossFit Tycoons, The First &amp; Only CrossFit Box in Alexandria and one of the fastest growing fitness entities in the Market. It came out this year with an amazing campaign encouraging and honoring their athletes who&rsquo;re going to compete in ElFit in a very creative way.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>We talked about &ldquo;Tycoons Tribe&rdquo; with&nbsp;3ashourz&nbsp;Tycoons Brand Manager/Partner and the former content creator for different leading Fitness entities like Cairo Runners, ElFit, CrossFit Stars and NTC+ Events.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>What&rsquo;s this campaign all about?</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;With lots of rockies and first-time competitors, it was all about making every single one look as cool as possible and allowing them to show off to their friends about their experiences -through series of instastory interviews- inspiring thousands of followers and new customers to participate and to compete. Also, it was about creating an unbreakable bond between them, as they were training in different locations and now they all train under the supervision of CF Tycoons Head Coach/Founder&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/loai_abdelkader/?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=1f7yu8hwrkrbq\">l</a>oai abdelkader&nbsp;&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>Do you think everyone can compete?&nbsp;</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em>CrossFit is all about competition as we understand this very well, that&rsquo;s why it became habit-forming for our members by casually pitting them against one another giving them something to compete over in regular training sessions and also in different community events such as Tycoons Games &amp; Fit For Good.&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>How do you see ElFit as a competition?</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Thanks to Adam and in the zone team. Elfit became one of the top competitions in the region and every year it gets better &amp; better. Last year, CrossFit Tycoons won the affiliate award with the highest number of participants and we had 2 podium finishers 3rd scaled female division&nbsp;aya<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/aya_mohamed_fouad/?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=mlusypi7tg5s\">&nbsp;</a>mohamed fouad &amp; 3rd female teen division&nbsp;arwa aboelata.<br />\r\nHopefully this year, We bring more competitors to the podium and defend our &ldquo;Affiliate Award&rdquo; title.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>What&rsquo;s your favorite marketing tactics?</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><em>In Sports Marketing, there&rsquo;s just so much to tap into. There&rsquo;s&nbsp;the human drama aspect, the underdog fighting his way to the top, the professional athlete making tremendous sacrifices. For me, one of my personal favorite is the community aspect, people coming together to participate in something greater than themselves.<br />\r\nAbove and beyond, the heart of what CrossFit Tycoons does best is storytelling.</em></p>\r\n', './images/news_images/Tycoons-MAin-696x364.jpg', './images/news_images/thumb/746891_resized214271.jpg', '2018-11-19 07:05:33', '2018-12-08 07:11:24', 4, '0', 0, 0),
