(151, 'Ali El-khatib', 'Coach', 'Progressive Calisthenics Certified Instructor,  Certified Physical Preparation Specialist,  SHP Program Design,  SHP Compound Exercise Analysis Course,  OPEX Movement and Assessment workshop.', './images/trainer/3f233653e70ebe48d28d131d378ad4d7.jpg', './images/trainer/thumb/resize_3f233653e70ebe48d28d131d378ad4d7.jpg', '', '', '', 7, 0, 'Trainer', '<p><em>Ali&#39;s passion for football can&#39;t go unnoticed, a football freak and a hardcore Manchester United fan. He always wanted to be a professional footballer, but failed to make it. In 2006, his relationship with lifting started to emerge, it didn&#39;t take much time for him to fall in love with the iron.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>In 2015, Khatib left his corporate job and took coaching as a professional career.&nbsp;He decided to blend his love for sports with strength and conditioning, so he can help current and future athletes achieve their health and performance goals.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>â€‹</em></p>\r\n', 95, NULL, '2018-12-01 09:12:13', '2018-12-29 10:51:09'),
