(160, 'Asser El-Sawaf', 'Coach', 'ISSA Personal Trainer Certification, CrossFit L1 & L2 Certified, CrossFit Weightlifting specialty course, SHP Program Design and Compound Exercise analysis Course, OPEX Movement and Assessment workshop.', './images/trainer/b19bda14b0180d273b524f0e0ba68ab7.png', './images/trainer/thumb/resize_b19bda14b0180d273b524f0e0ba68ab7.png', '', '', '', 0, 0, 'Trainer', '<p><em>Graduated with Bachelor Degree in Computer Engineering in 2011. Started his fitness career back in Alexandria in 2012 where he did his first certificate ISSA&#39;s CFT (Certified Fitness Trainer)</em></p>\r\n', 95, NULL, '2018-12-02 21:56:18', '2018-12-29 10:50:12'),
(161, 'Bahaa Hashim', NULL, NULL, './images/trainer/45ff88d7a6270a3d9b54abb3214772aa.png', './images/trainer/thumb/resize_45ff88d7a6270a3d9b54abb3214772aa.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'Trainer', NULL, 95, NULL, '2018-12-02 21:56:53', '2018-12-02 21:56:53'),
(162, 'Hisham Nassef', NULL, NULL, './images/trainer/cfce6bd1774001202e4ccd81ab2e0bb6.jpg', './images/trainer/thumb/resize_cfce6bd1774001202e4ccd81ab2e0bb6.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 'Trainer', NULL, 95, NULL, '2018-12-02 21:58:02', '2018-12-02 21:58:02'),
(163, 'Ismail El-Saidy', 'Coach', 'CrossFit Certified L1 Trainer,  ISSA Personal Trainer Certification,  Three courses in The English Football Association- England,  1st 4 sport Level 1 award in coaching (the first license in the FA),  FA child safeguarding,  FA First Emergency Aid.', './images/trainer/17facc70927bbca69b6cc937a912ce7b.jpg', './images/trainer/thumb/resize_17facc70927bbca69b6cc937a912ce7b.jpg', '', '', '', 1, 0, 'Trainer', '<p><em>Ismail started swimming at age 4. He also tried handball, basketball, Taekwondo and tennis till he joined the water polo team and it became his only sport activity for 11 years, reaching the first team and competing in several national competitions. Since then he started to be very committed to working-out and to playing football. He found passion in playing football and decided to fulfill this passion by entering the football coaching career by attending a football coaching course in London, 2014. Ismail also participated in a half marathon in 2014. By mid 2015 he became an assistant head coach in one of the known fitness training groups at Gezira Club. After a few months he led his own classes till he joined BeFit.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Ismail holds&nbsp;a BSC in International business and Finance and currently works&nbsp;at&nbsp;CIB as a Senior Credit Analyst.</em></p>\r\n', 95, NULL, '2018-12-02 21:59:02', '2018-12-29 10:47:50'),
(164, 'Karen El-Maalem', 'Coach', 'CrossFit Certified L1 Trainer', './images/trainer/c3b40e8ee0293665100c6b99427f2b75.jpg', './images/trainer/thumb/resize_c3b40e8ee0293665100c6b99427f2b75.jpg', '', '', '', 2, 0, 'Trainer', '<p><em>Having been born into an athletic family, we would have to say that her passion runs deep. She loves all the life lessons that can be learned through sports. Which is why she played tennis and soccer for 11 years. Currently she is a National Dodgeball Team Player. She participated in The World Cup in Manchester&rsquo;16 and getting ready for the coming one in NYC&rsquo;18. Karen has joined BeFit in 2016 for the Transformation Challenge. Ever since her life has changed physically and mentally.</em></p>\r\n', 95, NULL, '2018-12-02 21:59:27', '2018-12-29 10:40:36'),
(165, 'Malak El-Ayouty', 'Coach AND CO-FOUNDER OF BEFIT RECOVER. ', 'CrossFit Certified L1 & L2 Trainer  SHP Compound Exercise Analysis Course,  SHP Program Design Course , OPEX Movement and Assessment Workshop.', './images/trainer/010639ab362597c9b3a153bbeaaf21ab.jpg', './images/trainer/thumb/resize_010639ab362597c9b3a153bbeaaf21ab.jpg', '', '', '', 4, 0, 'Trainer', '<p><em>Malak comes with a wealth of experience; having played tennis for the best part of 10 years and have competed at a national level when she was 15 years old. Walking away from the sport, due to several injuries, never killed her passion for training and she found herself in functional fitness. Malak is also an avid cyclist and a mountain climber, she is also constantly looks for new ways to teach her mind and body to grow.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 95, NULL, '2018-12-02 22:00:22', '2018-12-29 10:38:41'),
