(174, 'Seif Tamimi', 'coach', 'CrossFit Certified L1 Trainer  SHP Compound Exercise Analysis Course,  SHP Program Design Course,   OPEX Movement and Assessment Workshop.', './images/trainer/9836eb5e0ccf4f6af20c992aa73f3a19.png', './images/trainer/thumb/resize_9836eb5e0ccf4f6af20c992aa73f3a19.png', '', '', '', 0, 0, 'Trainer', '<p><em>A full time coach and a part time surfer, He believes he should always be doing what he loves, and that&#39;s why coaching has been his thing since he was 19.<br />\r\nComing from a football background for more than a decade, and three years of CrossFit, he decided to take coaching as a career and pursue what he liked the most. On his free time, you can catch him surfing or just lying down by the beach.</em></p>\r\n', 95, NULL, '2018-12-02 22:16:17', '2018-12-29 10:36:09'),
